1) TEST Environment
	- 1 server with sync_server installed
	- 6 client on the same computer with server_client
	- 1 computer to launch the test
	
2) How to deploy
	a) install openerp on server with poc_addons and launch 
	b) install openerp on client with poc_addons and launch
	c) change test/config.py 
		i) change client_host client_port
		ii) change server_host server_port
	d) run init.py
		i) python init.py init  #to install all the db
		ii) python init.py module #to install all the required module
		
	to delete all the db: 
		
		python init.py clean
		
		
3) Registration 
once all the db are install and deploy, launch registration test :
This test registration and activation use case, mandatory to run other test

	python registration.py 

4) Data and message test
Use case supply 1-5
	
	python data_test.py
	
Use case message sync
	
	python message_test.py
